{"tid":1760421,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（有圖）有無手足比佢呃過錢","createTime":"2019-11-28T08:02:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T11:40:07.000Z","uid":333766,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0a23cd7048dc96cea49b571a3eab6c6224f50b9a","tid":1760421,"uid":333766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T08:02:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iU4A1Qe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiU4A1Qe.jpg&h=196a996b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0A6jJ3z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0A6jJ3z.jpg&h=74a8033c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4VCiZBV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4VCiZBV.jpg&h=efd49d27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢條撚樣之前借香港而家發生緊嘅事嚟扮可憐話跳樓<br />\n之後到最後俾人發現佢成日話跳樓都係搏可憐<br />\n之後就好多手足關心佢 佢就借題發揮成日話自己無錢/病左/交電話費嚟呃手足錢 仲要呃人感情呃埋男朋友啲錢（唔好歧視同性戀）<br />\n佢8月份個陣試過一腳踏7-8船全部無見過因為佢淨係貪啲會俾錢佢既人<br />\n佢成日都問佢啲網友（借）錢<br />\n～完～<br />\n純粹想問下有冇手足/其他人俾佢呃過錢"},{"pid":"439c19509aa46e4d04f63849a3efda73a6576e14","tid":1760421,"uid":66365,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T08:10:03.000Z","msg":"佢都有7-8船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bf729a0cd7eb1b006d77180c3edced5e54a4bd1","tid":1760421,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T08:43:26.000Z","msg":"似0仔<br />\n借錢俾佢個啲有無搞鳩人先"},{"pid":"bf5e7098783ca908bf41caa7ed32499a1dadab98","tid":1760421,"uid":333766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9bf729a0cd7eb1b006d77180c3edced5e54a4bd1","tid":1760421,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T08:43:26.000Z","msg":"似0仔<br />\n借錢俾佢個啲有無搞鳩人先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T09:00:54.000Z","msg":"無 因為借完俾佢佢會bloc